<h2><a name="append" id="append">append</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Składnia:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;string&gt;</span>
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> str <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span><span class="sy0">*</span> str <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> str<span class="sy0">,</span> size_type index<span class="sy0">,</span> size_type len <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span><span class="sy0">*</span> str<span class="sy0">,</span> size_type num <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> size_type num<span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
    string<span class="sy0">&amp;</span> append<span class="br0">&#40;</span> input_iterator start<span class="sy0">,</span> input_iterator end <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;</pre>
<p>
Funkcja append służy do:

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> (1&amp;2)dodawania <code>str</code> na koniec aktualnego stringa,</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> (3)dodawania fragmentu <code>str</code> od pozycji <code>index</code> o długości <code>len</code> znaków na koniec aktualnego stringa,</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> (4)dodawania pierwszych <code>num</code> znaków ze <code>str</code> na koniec aktualnego stringa,</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> (5)dodawania <code>num</code> powtórzeń znaku <code>ch</code> na koniec aktualnego stringa,</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> (6)dodawania fragmentu stringa zawartego między iteratorami <code>start</code> oraz <code>end</code> na koniec aktualnego stringa.</div>
</li>
</ul>

<p>

Przykładowo, poniższy kod wykorzystuje funkcję <code>append</code> do dodania 10 kopii znaku &#039;!&#039; do stringa:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">     <span class="kw4">string</span> str <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>;
     str.<span class="me1">append</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu0">10</span><span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="st0">'!'</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
     <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> str <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> endl;</pre>
<p>
Uruchomienie tego kodu spowoduje wyświetlenie się wiadomości:
</p>
<pre class="code">
     Hello World!!!!!!!!!!</pre>
<p>
W kolejnym przykładzie funkcja <code>append</code> została użyta do dołączenia fragmentu jednego stringa do drugiego:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">   <span class="kw4">string</span> str1 <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Eventually I stopped caring... &quot;</span>;
   <span class="kw4">string</span> str2 <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="st0">&quot;but that was the '80s so nobody noticed.&quot;</span>;
&nbsp;
   str1.<span class="me1">append</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> str2<span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="nu0">25</span><span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="nu0">15</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
   <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;str1 to: &quot;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> str1 <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> endl;</pre>
<p>
Powyższy kod wypisze następujący komunikat:
</p>
<pre class="code">
   str1 to: Eventually I stopped caring... nobody noticed.</pre>
</div>
